Brand marks — github, claude, chat_gpt (in ui/src/ui/icon.gleam)
================================================================================

Three icons in `ui/src/ui/icon.gleam` are third-party brand logos, not Lucide
geometry:

  github     GitHub's logo mark
  chat_gpt   OpenAI's ChatGPT mark
  claude     Anthropic's Claude mark

The `github`, `chat_gpt`, and `claude` marks are the GitHub, OpenAI, and Claude
logos as published by Simple Icons (https://simpleicons.org) under CC0 (public
domain). They are used only to label a link to a repository or an "open in this
service" action.

These logos are trademarks of their respective owners: the GitHub logo is a
